text: DXTE-TV, 21 (analog) and channel 18 (digital), is a commercial UHF television station. It is owned and operated by TV5 Network Inc.. Its studio, analog and digital transmitter are located at SMART Compound, Macapagal Drive, Upper Bulua, Cagayan de Oro City (near ABS-CBN). ==Digital channels== Channel Video Aspect Short name Programming Notes 21.01 480i 16:9 TV5 TV5 Cagayan de Oro Commercial free-to-air broadcast (10 kW) 21.02 480i 16:9 OnePH One PH 21.03 480i 4:3 One Sports One Sports Commercial free-to-air broadcast 21.35 240p 16:9 One Seg S1 TV5 Cagayan de Oro 1seg broadcast == Areas of coverage == === Primary areas === * Cagayan de Oro * Misamis Oriental ==== Secondary areas ==== * Camiguin * Portion of Bukidnon ==Related pages== *TV5 *List of television and radio stations owned by TV5 Network *Radyo5 101.5 News FM Cagayan De Oro ==References== Category:Filipino television stations Category:Television channels in Asia
